{"tid":1857983,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"讀完書出黎做野後，記住每月儲2650個口罩用黎投資","createTime":"2020-02-02T12:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T14:20:59.000Z","uid":4178,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"61fe5bba4d94854334772a708546461bd9988929","tid":1857983,"uid":4178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:27:37.000Z","msg":"當你 23歲讀完書出黎做野 <br />\n就算是但搵份全職既工作 <br />\n最少都有1萬2 （如下圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SiV4UVt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSiV4UVt.jpg&h=ba28a7c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cmGcjm9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcmGcjm9.jpg&h=907bb050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千奇唔好睇少呢萬2蚊 !!! </span></strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n由23歲 fresh grad 開始<br />\n你只要每個月儲起當中既 $3500 <br />\n學習長線價值投資買大約2650個口罩（市價65蚊50個口罩，如下圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGA6j9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGA6j9N.jpg&h=91342803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肯花花少少心機既，平均每年會有8厘 <strong><ins><span style=\"color: green;\">(+108%)</span></ins></strong> 合理回報 <br />\n<br />\n然後你一直每個月都持續儲起 $3500 去投資<br />\n<ins><strong>慢慢就會出現一件神奇既事</strong></ins> !!!!  (如下圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q2hiZqZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2hiZqZ.jpg&h=cd3422dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到你 61歲果陣<br />\n你會發現你戶口有 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>1083萬 </ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n去到呢步<br />\n你拎住呢 1083萬，可以繼續用原來既投資方法賺<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">+8%</span></strong> 利潤<br />\n即年收入達 86萬 （亦即是<ins><strong>月入7.2萬</strong></ins>）<br />\n其實你已經可以選擇退休，唔再需要為生活而工作<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你已經踏入了「財務自由」既狀態</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n就算你懶到連口罩都唔想買<br />\n你拎住1083萬，每個月拎$23000 出黎作生活費 <br />\n哇屌，你都要39年時間<br />\n直至 （61+39 = <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>100歲</ins></strong></span>）先用得晒筆錢呀陰公！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之聽我講<br />\n堅持每個月儲起2650個口罩用作投資 <br />\n你第時老左就會多謝我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb88d11a5aa3280b8440dc890a6df17c9efe64f8","tid":1857983,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d66081b65d12c8e8a796e846420d897c9c9df8","tid":1857983,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:32:58.000Z","msg":"口罩會過期"},{"pid":"087800fe771eee802633fd42ee48f322669bb5c7","tid":1857983,"uid":34828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:37:36.000Z","msg":"諗住會連去做黨主席嗰篇文，點知冇"},{"pid":"955034b4d2f438e42ce5c849e4f84a400fc0bad1","tid":1857983,"uid":141625,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"最尾發現口罩過期 此post已完"},{"pid":"4a92d308184acf22b82494c69089cbbbc83e858c","tid":1857983,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"以前做口罩公司話唔會過期<br />\n冇fc"},{"pid":"3223355602bc5201118c333f947ee3eb06e07afb","tid":1857983,"uid":240028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:45:11.000Z","msg":"你估年年都要咁全世界戴口罩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />此post已完"},{"pid":"921d10db9f465d